insights.rationale: With a strong presence of trailers from well-known series and films, there is potential for increased viewership through exclusive behind-the-scenes content or extended trailers.
Given the popularity of live streaming, integrating interactive components can enhance engagement and drive repeat viewership.
Re-releases and adaptations of classic games can attract both newer audiences and nostalgic fans, providing a dual-market approach.
Expanding into regional and culturally diverse content can tap into new audience demographics, enhancing market penetration and reach.
